  m_Name: QuestionChoice1
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::QuestionChoiceData
  Question: The Wolf, now calmed by Gilded Flute, leans in and whispers, "Your garden
    is so beautiful, Celestial Weaver. Where do you go when the sun rises? I want
    to visit you there."
  option1: "I\u2019m glad you like the garden, but I don\u2019t share my home address
    with anyone without my guardian\u2019s permission."
  option2: I live in the golden wheat fields just past the cypress trees; come find
    me tomorrow!
  option3: "I can\u2019t tell you, but if you follow the swirling stars, they might
    lead you to my door."
